visual.name: barOfPieChartTest
visual.description: The Bar of Pie is an extremely handy visual, since it allows you to shift the smaller slices of the pie to a separate stacked bar chart. The Bar of Pie also supports Subgrouping to add a stacked bar chart subcategory for each slice. Visit https://datellers.com/bar-of-pie-a-power-bi-cutsom-visual-by-datellers/ to learn more!
